Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.75,0:00:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.75,0:00:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翌晨的陽光就快來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.89,0:00:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照進這間充滿煙蒂\N雜亂無章的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.70,0:00:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Tell me why 聖母瑪利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.77,0:00:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對溫柔感到飢渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.04,0:00:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Tell me why
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.74,0:00:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼孤單的夜晚\N總是如此漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.65,0:00:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牛仔褲下的膝蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.52,0:00:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被破碎的夢想打溼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.89,0:01:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿著襯衫的胸部太過耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.86,0:01:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.82,0:01:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.39,0:01:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.36,0:01:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.50,0:01:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安,今天也要去找工作嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.24,0:01:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.20,0:01:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好辛苦喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.27,0:01:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我找到工作\N八神應該也會死心回家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.95,0:02:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟一直這樣下去也不是辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.72,0:02:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.82,0:02:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請好好加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.29,0:02:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.96,0:02:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-哎呀\N-怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.29,0:02:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的領帶歪歪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.00,0:02:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.00,0:02:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.47,0:02:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你忘了東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.50,0:02:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,手帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.07,0:02:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可以忘了\N昨晚我還特地燙好拿出來放呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.07,0:02:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.14,0:02:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看,領帶歪歪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.21,0:02:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了啦,又沒有歪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,轉過身來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.98,0:02:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是不會照顧自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那,管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.25,0:02:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,快走快走,會遲到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.66,0:02:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早點回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.40,0:02:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#74 就職戰線出現異狀!\N五代的再見大逆轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.37,0:02:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,有電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.08,0:02:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,不好意思,你接一下好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.64,0:03:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在手邊很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.71,0:03:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,這裡是八神家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.25,0:03:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,老師\N小女平時承蒙您的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼晚了真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.36,0:03:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你女兒伊吹\N最近因為感冒都沒有來上學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.20,0:03:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我聽到了一些傳言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼傳言?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.41,0:03:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的感冒根本是騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.51,0:03:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實她跟某個男人同居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.18,0:03:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.12,0:03:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.55,0:03:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.19,0:03:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我想向本人確定一下\N才打電話來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.52,0:03:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊吹在家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.23,0:03:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在,只是她重感冒\N一直臥病在床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.77,0:04:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就如您所聽到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.44,0:04:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,居然已經傳出\N這種傳聞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.61,0:04:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總不能這樣一直敷衍下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我能怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.05,0:04:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要把她帶回來\N不然會被退學的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.09,0:04:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我知道,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.03,0:04:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,在你幫五代老師\N找到工作之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就不回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.47,0:04:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今,就算我再有本事\N也無法讓五代進入三友商事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.21,0:04:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,介紹其它的公司不行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.08,0:04:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它的公司?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.18,0:04:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果啊,那家店的老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直盯著我瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.78,0:04:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還說我像新婚的新娘子\N算我便宜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,去沖杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.66,0:04:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,對了,櫃子裡的書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.49,0:04:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我賣給撿破爛的\N換了很多錢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.50,0:05:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,砂糖放到哪裡去了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.33,0:05:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託,妳安靜點行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.94,0:05:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,打破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歐巴桑來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.38,0:05:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.11,0:05:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,聽說你今天也出去找工作啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.82,0:05:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.68,0:05:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,在寫履歷表啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.22,0:05:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種東西寫幾張都沒用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.29,0:05:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊,還是早點死心比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.33,0:05:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且把這女孩當人質的作戰\N對她父親好像也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.97,0:05:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不要瞧不起人了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.20,0:05:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才沒期望能靠她爸爸找到工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.80,0:05:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會靠自己的力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.74,0:05:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代怎麼看都不像是個\N會有光明人生的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.61,0:05:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.65,0:05:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是個可憐的青年啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.68,0:05:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正忘了找工作的事\N痛痛快快喝一頓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛快的喝!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.39,0:05:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不要鬧了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通通給我出去,快啊,出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.86,0:06:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不允許任何人打擾五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.67,0:06:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些人真的很討厭\N每天晚上都跑來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.84,0:06:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們把這個房間當作什麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實在太沒常識了,沒常識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.85,0:06:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.21,0:06:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟妳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.95,0:06:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.48,0:06:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論出了什麼事\N我都站在你這一邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.72,0:06:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要是我辦得到的事\N儘管說沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳能不能稍微安靜一點?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.97,0:06:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.72,0:07:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託,妳這樣一直盯著看\N我反而更不能專心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.59,0:07:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.76,0:07:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係,知道就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.10,0:07:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是愛的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.10,0:07:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像這樣看著心愛之人的背影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.14,0:07:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安安靜靜地睡覺時\N倒是蠻可愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.56,0:07:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.60,0:07:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.80,0:07:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.37,0:08:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明天要去找她爸爸談清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.10,0:08:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公,我要先睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.81,0:08:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可不要喝太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.81,0:08:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的確可以在跟三友商事相關的\N中小企業幫他介紹個工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.86,0:08:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這樣也算是個父親嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.33,0:08:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女兒明明住在一個年輕男人家裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.84,0:08:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然不來把她帶回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.77,0:09:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你身為父親的責任到底在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.18,0:09:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天一定要把話說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.35,0:09:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.62,0:09:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正我早就對三友商事死心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.35,0:09:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有必要對八神的父親\N唯唯諾諾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.13,0:09:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.49,0:09:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.57,0:09:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.77,0:09:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裡,不好意思\N白天還把您叫出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.27,0:09:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.00,0:09:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你找我有什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.13,0:10:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.77,0:10:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你現在還沒資格叫我爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.51,0:10:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不管有沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.97,0:10:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之,我真的很頭痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是當然的囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.81,0:10:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憑你唸的那所大學的程度\N想找好工作是很難的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.05,0:10:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是在說找工作的事\N而是你寶貝千金的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.79,0:10:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我女兒的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.16,0:10:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不覺得你女兒很可憐嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.76,0:10:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她這樣一直住在我那裡\N對我來說也很困擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.07,0:10:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\N你的意思是我女兒打擾到你嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老實說,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.91,0:10:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這種人,居然在發現\N無法利用伊吹找到工作後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.44,0:10:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就開始嫌她麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你實在太卑劣了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開玩笑了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡的是管理員!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.09,0:11:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問您要點什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.76,0:11:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冰咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.13,0:11:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的,馬上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.93,0:11:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你剛才說的是真的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.37,0:11:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的,所以我打從一開始\N就沒有想要利用你女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.71,0:11:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個伊吹知道嗎?\N她知道你的心意嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.44,0:11:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她很清楚,但就是不死心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.05,0:11:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.28,0:11:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以\N拜託你早點把你女兒帶回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.19,0:11:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼,事情很簡單嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.42,0:12:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想利用她父親這層關係的想法\N也不能說完全沒有想過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.69,0:12:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,不行\N我得靠自己的力量找到工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.93,0:12:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天去學校的就業輔導處\N問問看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.58,0:12:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,快來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.74,0:12:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.58,0:12:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火災,火災,在你的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.35,0:12:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.55,0:12:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火災,發生火災了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.29,0:12:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?火災?在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.62,0:12:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,快來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.72,0:12:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.54,0:12:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秋刀魚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.38,0:13:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.39,0:13:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秋刀魚不知是苦還是鹹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.12,0:13:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連我的房間都烏煙瘴氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.96,0:13:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,幸好不是火災
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.20,0:13:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火災?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.66,0:13:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.17,0:13:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,驚擾到你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.20,0:13:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,道歉就沒事了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.94,0:13:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在一個沒有抽油煙機的房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.34,0:13:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,烤秋刀魚會怎麼樣\N這點小事妳會不知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.84,0:13:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我一定饒不了妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在立刻搬出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.21,0:13:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是想烤當季的秋刀魚給你吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.65,0:13:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你卻叫我搬出去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.86,0:13:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好狠心的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.43,0:13:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能被她那雙眼睛騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.26,0:13:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正妳今天一定要回家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.77,0:13:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.84,0:14:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.84,0:14:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今,我根本回不去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.95,0:14:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這妳不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.48,0:14:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我跟妳爸爸見過面\N已經都談好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.59,0:14:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟我爸見面?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.09,0:14:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他現在一定在家裡等妳回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.09,0:14:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這樣的話,你的工作…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.33,0:14:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我懂了,連工作的事也談好了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.53,0:14:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此,用女兒回家當作條件\N請他幫忙找工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代也挺厲害的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.41,0:14:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.18,0:14:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰要那種不明事理的老頭\N幫忙找工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.38,0:14:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要靠自己的力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.39,0:14:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊\N五代每天都很努力在找工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.19,0:14:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過全都吃了閉門羹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.86,0:15:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.57,0:15:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉,打擾了你們談話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.94,0:15:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白天很謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.97,0:15:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.87,0:15:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要,我不要回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.14,0:15:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.01,0:15:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.11,0:15:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼都別說,你收下這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.05,0:15:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們子公司的介紹信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.59,0:15:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,介紹信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.72,0:15:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要帶這封介紹信去\N一定能夠被錄取的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.46,0:15:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.60,0:15:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你之間有很多誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這只是表示我的一點歉意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.00,0:15:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就開心的收下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.74,0:15:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走,伊吹,跟爸爸回家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.34,0:15:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果妳不回去的話\N這件事就會被取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.75,0:15:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這關係到五代的將來\N伊吹,妳打算怎麼做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.33,0:16:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉,這麼晚來打擾各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裡,別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.80,0:16:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.87,0:16:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代老師,過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.34,0:16:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊?什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.51,0:16:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千萬不要忘了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.41,0:16:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我暫時讓步\N你才能找到工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.55,0:16:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我走了,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.22,0:16:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊吹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.85,0:16:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,快走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.39,0:16:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.49,0:16:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真要命,那孩子真的很麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.06,0:16:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,五代也等於找到工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.07,0:16:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來喝酒提前慶祝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.21,0:16:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,妳也來喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.61,0:16:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.60,0:17:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們說要提前慶祝你找到工作\N走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.85,0:17:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的工作內定了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.68,0:17:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一家電腦相關的小公司\N叫“擔商會”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒聽過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.79,0:17:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這兩三年才急速成長的公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.73,0:17:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說急速成長的公司\N特別容易倒閉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.16,0:17:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也拜託一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.37,0:17:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,沒想到你居然會是\N第一個找到工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.27,0:17:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是憑實力,實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.94,0:17:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真敢說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.78,0:18:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也差不多該認真找工作了\N不然你又要再等一年了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.91,0:18:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無所謂,頂多留級一年就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不像某人\N沒有必要急著找工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.72,0:18:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫時會兩個人都去工作嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.59,0:18:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果可以的話\N我希望能靠我的薪水養活兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.36,0:18:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想得真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.63,0:18:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然不是學生\N家裡就不會寄錢來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.27,0:18:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小公司的薪水也很少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.27,0:18:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一個人吃就已經差不多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.51,0:18:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你居然能想得這麼悲觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.44,0:18:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼樂觀的材料嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.91,0:18:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.88,0:18:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員應該是個\N很能忍受貧窮的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.63,0:18:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我問你\N這世上有喜歡貧窮的女人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.83,0:18:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有說喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.34,0:19:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是我覺得她很勤儉刻苦\N應該很懂得持家理財
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.34,0:19:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算剛開始只是住在\N六塊榻榻米大的公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.35,0:19:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起喔,響子\N我的薪水不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.82,0:19:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,別這麼說\N我喜歡這種清儉的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.29,0:19:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為房間很小\N我才能一直依偎在你身邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.06,0:19:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝妳,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳真的好體貼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.37,0:19:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.51,0:19:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的腦漿一定是玫瑰色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.31,0:19:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,部長,聽說日和產業很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.62,0:19:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的情況究竟如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.42,0:19:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,如果演變成連鎖破產的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.96,0:19:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的子公司\N也會受到很大的打擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.66,0:19:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然做了很多補救措施…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.76,0:19:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是沒救嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.43,0:20:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,事到如今只好捨棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.67,0:20:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.14,0:20:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然想到一件事有點掛心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什麼事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.55,0:20:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了,既然想不起來\N那就表示不是什麼重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.85,0:20:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也真是愛自尋煩惱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.62,0:20:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣,今晚陪我去喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.43,0:20:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊,我很樂意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.00,0:20:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.87,0:20:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手續都順利完成了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,託妳的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.64,0:20:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.74,0:20:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點小東西\N恭喜你找到工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.08,0:20:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不好意思\N還讓妳這樣費心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.05,0:20:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以打開來看嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.19,0:20:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊,只是便宜的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.62,0:21:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會是什麼呢?好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.16,0:21:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇,是領帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.83,0:21:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出了社會之後\N有幾條領帶都不會嫌多的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.40,0:21:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.54,0:21:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打上這條領帶\N好像會出人頭地似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有這回事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.95,0:21:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,我不是說\N你不會出人頭地的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.55,0:21:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳好好期待吧,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.55,0:21:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會拼命工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.82,0:21:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,比起那種大公司…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.29,0:21:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在小公司工作\N比較會有機會擔當重任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.63,0:21:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在小公司工作,也比較容易升官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.37,0:21:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我拿到第一個月的薪水\N我再回送妳東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.17,0:21:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這怎麼好意思呢\N你的薪水又不高…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.01,0:21:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.82,0:22:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.82,0:22:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.83,0:22:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像不被期待的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.13,0:22:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨,社會人士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.27,0:22:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛一個人悶悶的坐在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.14,0:22:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又要喝酒嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.30,0:22:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然要喝囉\N慶祝你找到工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.54,0:22:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚要不客氣的大喝特喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.81,0:22:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們什麼時候客氣過了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.45,0:22:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,杯子杯子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.95,0:22:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.78,0:22:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先別管這個\N你趕快去管理員室吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.32,0:22:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了今晚的宴會\N她好像親手做了很多料理喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.53,0:22:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還笑咪咪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.83,0:22:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.53,0:22:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.54,0:22:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來得正好\N幫我端菜上去好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.41,0:23:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇,好豐盛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.25,0:23:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先偷吃一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.15,0:23:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.42,0:23:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思,幫我把電視關掉好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.78,0:23:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.62,0:23:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一則新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.42,0:23:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠著開發電腦軟體急速成長的\N日和產業倒閉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.69,0:23:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連帶受到衝擊的相關企業有\N理參電器、輕井商事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.10,0:23:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及擔商會\N都被迫捲入連鎖破產的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.23,0:23:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以上是今天的新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.44,0:23:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才是不是有提到擔商會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.48,0:23:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.39,0:23:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?明日菜她?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.53,0:23:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得了相思病!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.96,0:23:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說一直臥病在床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.10,0:23:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代\N現在不是聊這種八卦的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.87,0:23:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,八神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.04,0:23:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.60,0:24:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『專一的愛情!八神和明日菜\N是學不會教訓的女人』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.17,0:24:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又離家出走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.42,0:24:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人坐在黎明的護欄上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.94,0:24:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至今一直在尋找遺落愛的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.65,0:24:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.86,0:24:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳…一陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.26,0:25:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目光交會…只有…再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.27,0:25:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.44,0:25:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…在雨中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.87,0:25:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忽然…胸口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.28,0:25:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢…濡濕而發光

